<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Refund' }) %>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/loader') %>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  
  <main>
      <section class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2>Refund Policy</h2>
          <p>Important information about refunds for digital products.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid" style="max-width: 880px;">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>1. General Policy</h3>
            <p>
              All products sold by Armora Cheats are digital, time‑limited or
              lifetime licenses. Because access is granted immediately and
              cannot be “returned”, all sales are generally considered final.
            </p>

            <h3>2. Non‑Refundable Situations</h3>
            <p>We typically do NOT offer refunds in the following cases:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Once a license key has been delivered or activated.</li>
              <li>
                If your account or hardware ID is banned, restricted, or flagged
                by a game, anti‑cheat, or third party.
              </li>
              <li>For performance issues related to your own PC or internet.</li>
              <li>
                For misuse, violations of our Terms of Service, or attempts to
                share / resell access.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <h3>3. Exceptional Cases</h3>
            <p>
              In rare situations (for example, duplicate purchases or clear
              payment errors), we may consider partial or full refunds at our
              sole discretion. Proof of purchase and identity may be required.
            </p>

            <h3>4. Third‑Party Resellers</h3>
            <p>
              If you purchased access from an authorized reseller, their refund
              rules may apply in addition to ours. You may need to contact the
              reseller directly regarding payment disputes.
            </p>

            <h3>5. Chargebacks</h3>
            <p>
              Unauthorized chargebacks or payment disputes may result in
              immediate suspension of your license, account blacklisting, and
              refusal of future service.
            </p>

            <h3>6. Contact</h3>
            <p>
              If you believe you qualify for a refund under this Policy, please
              contact support with as much detail as possible (payment proof,
              date, and reason). We will review your request, but approval is
              not guaranteed.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
